{"ID":270366, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"366\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs365.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs367.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 366<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">the cannon and muskets in Missouri, I was unarmed. God will always protect me<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> until my mission\n  is fulfilled.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I calculate to be one of the instruments of setting up the kingdom of Daniel<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> by the word of the\n  Lord,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> and I intend to lay a foundation<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> that will revolutionize the whole world. I once offered my\n  life<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> to the Missouri mob as a sacrifice for my people, and here I am. It will not be by sword or gun\n  that this kingdom will roll on: the power of truth is such that all nations will be under the necessity\n  of obeying<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> the Gospel. The prediction is that army will be against army:<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> it may be that the Saints\n  will have to beat their ploughs into swords,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> for it will not do for men to sit down patiently and see\n  their children destroyed.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Resurrection<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">My text is on the resurrection of the dead, which you will find in the 14th chapter of John&mdash;&ldquo;In\n  my Father&rsquo;s house are many mansions.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> It should be&mdash;&ldquo;In my Father&rsquo;s kingdom are many\n  kingdoms,&rdquo; in order that ye may be heirs of God and joint-heirs with me.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> I do not believe the\n  Methodist doctrine of sending honest men and noble-minded men to hell, along with the murderer<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span>\n  and the adulterer.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> They may hurl all their hell and fiery billows<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> upon me, for they will roll off me\n  as fast as they come on. But I have an order of things<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> to save the poor fellows at any rate, and get\n  them saved; for I will send men to preach to them in prison<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> and save them if I can.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Salvation for the Dead<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">There are mansions for those who obey a celestial law,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> and there are other mansions for those\n  who come short<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> of the law every man in his own order.<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> There is baptism for those to exercise\n  who are alive,<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> and baptism for the dead<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> who die without the knowledge of the Gospel.<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I am going on in my progress for eternal life.<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> It is not only necessary that you should be\n  baptized for your dead,<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span> but you will have to go through all the ordinances for them, the same as\n  you have gone through to save yourselves.<span class=\"footRef\">26<\/span> There will be 144,000<span class=\"footRef\">27<\/span> saviors<span class=\"footRef\">28<\/span> on Mount Zion,<span class=\"footRef\">29<\/span> and\n  with them an innumerable host that no man can number.<span class=\"footRef\">30<\/span> Oh! I beseech you to go forward,<span class=\"footRef\">31<\/span> go\n  forward and make your calling and your election sure;<span class=\"footRef\">32<\/span> and if any man preach any other Gospel\n  than that which I have preached, he shall be cursed;<span class=\"footRef\">33<\/span> and some of you who now hear<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112537\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112537)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112537)\">3 Ne. 4:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115877\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115877)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115877)\">D&amp;C 122:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107519\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107519)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107519)\">Dan. 2:44<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106384\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106384)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106384)\">1 Sam. 3:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106447\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106447)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106447)\">1 Kgs. 13:1,5,9,18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106686\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106686)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106686)\">Ps. 33:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107112\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107112)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107112)\">Isa. 28:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113076\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113076)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113076)\">D&amp;C 1:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116046\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116046)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116046)\">D&amp;C 124:118<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116603\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" oncli